attorneys: Motion of the Special Master for allowance of fees and disbursements is granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $213,547.35 for the period September 1, 2016, through December 31, 2016, to be paid equally by the parties.
casebody.head_matter:
FLORIDA, plaintiff,
v.
GEORGIA.
No. 142, Original.
Supreme Court of the United States
Feb. 21, 2017.
Motion of the Special Master for allowance of fees and disbursements is granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $213,547.35 for the period September 1, 2016, through December 31, 2016, to be paid equally by the parties.
